ame=\"2020Dates\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/spider-man-universe-movies-2020-sony-1203034837/ |title=Sony Dates Two Marvel Movies for 2020 |last=Donnelly |first=Matt |date=November 21, 2018 |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/746YLDNzS?url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/spider-man-universe-movies-2020-sony-1203034837/ |archive-date=November 21, 2018 |access-date=November 22, 2018 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WorkingTitle\">{{Cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2018/11/22/morbius-living-vampire-working-title/ |title='Morbius The Living Vampire' Working Title Revealed |last=Mueller |first=Matthew |date=November 22, 2018 |website=ComicBook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181126231334/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2018/11/22/morbius-living-vampire-working-title/ |archive-date=November 26, 2018 |access-date=November 27, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Arjona\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/morbius-movie-casts-adria-arjona-as-martine-bancroft-1169668 |title='Morbius': Adria Arjona in Early Talks to Join Jared Leto |last=Couch |first=Aaron |date=December 14, 2018 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215104057/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/morbius-movie-casts-adria-arjona-as-martine-bancroft-1169668 |archive-date=December 15, 2018 |access-date=December 15, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Smith\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/matt-smith-jared-leto-morbius-1203114661/ |title=Matt Smith to Star With Jared Leto in Marvel Spinoff \u2018Morbius\u2019 (Exclusive) |last=Kroll |first=Justin |date=January 24, 2019 |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125061054/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/matt-smith-jared-leto-morbius-1203114661/ |archive-date=January 25, 2019 |access-dat