68921/ |title=Jared Harris Joins Jared Leto In Sony\u2019s \u2018Spider-Man\u2019 Spinoff \u2018Morbius\u2019 |last=N'Duka |first=Amanda |date=March 4, 2019 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190305065844/https://deadline.com/2019/03/jared-harris-jared-leto-sony-morbius-1202568921/ |archive-date=March 5, 2019 |access-date=March 10, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Gibson\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/tyrese-gibson-morbius-jared-leto-marvel-1203155757/ |title=Tyrese Gibson Joins Jared Leto in Marvel Spinoff \u2018Morbius\u2019 (Exclusive) |last=Kroll |first=Justin |date=March 5, 2019 |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306094857/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/tyrese-gibson-morbius-jared-leto-marvel-1203155757/ |archive-date=March 6, 2019 |access-date=March 10, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Gibson2\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tyrese-gibson-talks-join-jared-leto-spider-man-spinoff-morbius-1192546 |title=Tyrese Gibson in Talks to Join Jared Leto in Spider-Man Spinoff 'Morbius' |last=Kit |first=Borys |date=March 5, 2019 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306070558/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tyrese-gibson-talks-join-jared-leto-spider-man-spinoff-morbius-1192546 |archive-date=March 6, 2019 |access-date=March 10, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SmithLAMar2019\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-matt-smith-mapplethorpe-charlie-says-20190307-story.html |title=Matt Smith leaves \u2018The Crown\u2019 behind for Charles Manson and Robert Mapplethorpe |last=Zemler |first=Emily |date=March 5, 2019 |website=[[Los Angeles Times]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190307143652/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-matt-smith-mapplethorpe-charlie-says-20