ang|first=Brent|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=September 27, 2019|access-date=September 27, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927160452/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/sony-marvel-tom-holland-spider-man-1203351489/|archive-date=September 27, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"DeadlineSonyMarvelDealSM3\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/sony-walt-disneys-marvel-team-on-third-spider-man-homecoming-title-with-superhero-to-appear-in-future-marvel-pics-1202746497/|title=Spider-Man Back In Action As Sony Agrees To Disney Co-Fi For New Movie, Return To MCU: How Spidey\u2019s Web Got Untangled|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=September 27, 2019|accessdate=September 27, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927174504/https://deadline.com/2019/09/sony-walt-disneys-marvel-team-on-third-spider-man-homecoming-title-with-superhero-to-appear-in-future-marvel-pics-1202746497/|archive-date=September 27, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Synopsis\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cbr.com/morbius-sony-spider-verse-synopsis/|title=Morbius: Sony Releases Spider-Verse Vampire Film's Official Summary|last=Ramirez II|first=Hector|website=[[Comic Book Resources]]|date=January 14, 2020|accessdate=January 18, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115143400/https://www.cbr.com/morbius-sony-spider-verse-synopsis/|archive-date=January 15, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MarcumHolloway\">{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2020/01/14/morbius-trailer-iron-man-writers-script-rewrite-art-marcum-matt-holloway/|title=Morbius Taps Iron Man Writers for Rewrites|last=Barnhardt|first=Adam|website=ComicBook.com|date=January 13, 2020|accessdate=January 18, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114065848/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2020/01/14/morbius-trailer-iron-man-writers-script-rewrite-art-marcum-matt-holloway/|archive-date=January 14, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>